					<h2><a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/2012/10/13/the-nobel-wtf-prize-azizonomics/">The Nobel WTF Prize&nbsp;[Azizonomics]</a></h2>

					<div class="post-info">
						<p>
							<span class="time">October 13, 2012</span>
															<span class="author">by <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/author/mktgeistmike/" title="Posts by mktgeistmike" rel="author">mktgeistmike</a></span>
																						<span class="post-comments"><a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/2012/10/13/the-nobel-wtf-prize-azizonomics/#respond" title="Comment on The Nobel WTF Prize&nbsp;[Azizonomics]">Leave a comment</a></span>
																				</p>
					</div>

					<p>So the European Union won the Nobel Peace prize <a href="http://maxkeiser.com/2012/10/12/the-nobel-wtf-prize/%22The%20Nobel%20Peace%20Prize%202012%22">for</a> “having over six decades contributed to the advancement of peace and reconciliation, democracy and human rights in Europe.”</p>
<p><a href="http://azizonomics.files.wordpress.com/2012/10/nobel_prize.jpeg"><img alt="" src="http://azizonomics.files.wordpress.com/2012/10/nobel_prize.jpeg?w=342&#038;h=256" height="256" width="342" /></a></p>
