			<div class="post-7163 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-ecb category-europe">

				<div class="entry">

					<h2><a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/2012/09/27/the-ecb-managed-to-increase-broad-money-supply-in-the-eurozone-but-is-unable-to-improve-credit-conditions-soberlook/">The ECB managed to increase broad money supply in the Eurozone but is unable to improve credit conditions&nbsp;[SoberLook]</a></h2>

					<div class="post-info">
						<p>
							<span class="time">September 27, 2012</span>
															<span class="author">by <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/author/mktgeistmike/" title="Posts by mktgeistmike" rel="author">mktgeistmike</a></span>
																						<span class="post-comments"><a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/2012/09/27/the-ecb-managed-to-increase-broad-money-supply-in-the-eurozone-but-is-unable-to-improve-credit-conditions-soberlook/#respond" title="Comment on The ECB managed to increase broad money supply in the Eurozone but is unable to improve credit conditions&nbsp;[SoberLook]">Leave a comment</a></span>
																				</p>
					</div>

					<p>The ECB&#8217;s massive balance sheet expansion during the past year succeeded in generating growth in the euro area&#8217;s broad money supply.</p>
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="center">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td><a href="http://mktgeist.files.wordpress.com/2012/09/ecbbalancesheet.png?w=300"><img src="http://mktgeist.files.wordpress.com/2012/09/ecbbalancesheet.png?w=300" alt="" border="0" /></a></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>ECB balance sheet (€mm)</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<p>However the increase in money supply is yet to translate into material growth in credit. The two indicators have diverged.</p>
<p><a href="http://soberlook.com/2012/09/the-ecb-managed-to-increase-broad-money.html">Read more</a></p>
